### SECTION 1: NOTIFICATIONS RBAC

### 1. [SHOULD 201] POST: Admin creates a notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campId": 1,
  "userId": null,
  "targetRole": "WORKER",
  "type": "INVENTORY_ALERT",
  "title": "RBAC notification test",
  "message": "Admin-created notification for RBAC validation",
  "read": false,
  "createdDate": "2026-04-06T00:00:00Z",
  "readDate": null,
  "sourceType": "RBAC_TEST",
  "sourceId": null
}

###

### 2. [SHOULD 403] POST: Worker attempts to create a notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campId": 1,
  "userId": null,
  "targetRole": "WORKER",
  "type": "INVENTORY_ALERT",
  "title": "RBAC forbidden test",
  "message": "Worker create attempt should be forbidden",
  "read": false,
  "createdDate": "2026-04-06T00:00:00Z",
  "readDate": null,
  "sourceType": "RBAC_TEST",
  "sourceId": null
}

###

### 3. [SHOULD 200] GET: Worker gets all notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###

### 4. [SHOULD 200] PUT: Worker marks their OWN notification as read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "read": true
}

###

### 5. [SHOULD 403] PUT: Worker tries to mark someone ELSE'S notification as read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "read": true
}

###

### 6. [SHOULD 403] DELETE: Admin tries to delete a notification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### =========================================
### AUTOMATION - GLOBAL NOTIFICATION AUDIT
### =========================================

### [NOTIF-AUTO-01] List automated notifications for message validation
### Validate the following titles in results:
### - "Alerta de inventario bajo"
### - "Asignacion de expedicion"
### - "Role Updated"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=1&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
